ActInternational Development Research Centre Act
PrecisAppointment of DENIS DESAUTELS of Ottawa, Ontario, to be a governor of the Board of Governors of the International Development Research Centre, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, effective January 2, 2006, in the place of Tom McKay.
